    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Exists.choose#doc\">docs#Exists.choose</a> likely composed with <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=ExistsUnique.exists#doc\">docs#ExistsUnique.exists</a></p>",
